The paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques to extract tables from documents, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) and genetic algorithms also suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.CL, cs.DL) and optimization (cs.LG) sub-categories.
